{"article_id":"ijZnChQ7h1bePk61","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Congress faces an end-of-the-year deadline or `` fiscal cliff ''","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Massive spending cuts are scheduled to kick in","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"and tax breaks begin to expire","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Both parties agree","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Tuesday 's vote was a mandate","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"to compromise ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"avoid the fiscal cliff","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"But party leaders continue to sharply disagree over the key issue of top tax rates","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"A day after an election","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that both parties agreed","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"was a mandate","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"to find compromise","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"and avoid the so-called fiscal cliff ,","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"Democratic and Republican congressional leaders also continued to sharply disagree over the key issue","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"of whether top tax rates should be raised","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"to help resolve the looming crisis .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Republicans said","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"higher rates would damage the economy ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"while Democrats said","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"it was the only equitable way","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"to tackle the debt .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Congress faces an end-of-the-year deadline","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"before massive spending cuts kick in","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"and tax breaks begin to expire ,","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"including the Bush-era tax cuts at the end of December .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"The fiscal cliff also includes so-called sequestration","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"-- automatic across-the-board spending cuts","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"set to trigger at the beginning of 2013","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"if Capitol Hill fails to create a deficit-reduction plan .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"In a formal speech on Capitol Hill Wednesday , House Speaker John Boehner sounded conciliatory","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"even as he made it clear","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"higher tax rates would be unacceptable to Republicans","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"who control the House .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"'Fiscal cliff ' could bring recession","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"MUST WATCH 'Fiscal cliff ' could bring recession","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"01:56","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"What must happen","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"to avoid 'fiscal cliff '","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"MUST WATCH What must happen","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"to avoid 'fiscal cliff '","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"01:53","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Back to business for Obama","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"MUST WATCH Back to business for Obama","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"06:10","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"Dems , GOP talk 'fiscal cliff ' future","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":15},{"id":54,"text":"MUST WATCH Dems , GOP talk 'fiscal cliff ' future 03:42 `` For the purposes","depth":18},{"id":55,"text":"of forging a bipartisan agreement","depth":19},{"id":56,"text":"that begins to solve the problem ,","depth":19},{"id":57,"text":"we 're willing to accept new revenue , under the right conditions , ''","depth":17},{"id":58,"text":"Boehner said .","depth":16},{"id":59,"text":"The speaker then insisted","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"the revenue come from `` a growing economy ,","depth":15},{"id":61,"text":"energized by a simpler , cleaner , fair tax code , with fewer loopholes and lower rates for all , ''","depth":15},{"id":62,"text":"and not from higher rates on higher earners .","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"As part of a broader compromise , Boehner said","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"that tax reform must be coupled with `` concrete steps","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"to put our country 's entitlement programs on a sounder financial footing . ''","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"A Senate Democratic leadership aide complained","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"Boehner 's approach on revenue","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"-- which might not require the wealthy to pay more --","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"was `` insufficient ''","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"and would not raise enough money","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"to have a significant impact on the deficit .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Earlier Wednesday , Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid said","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"that he and Boehner had a `` pleasant conversation '' by phone","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"and that he did n't expect either man to `` draw any lines in the sand '' ahead of negotiations .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"But Reid insisted several times","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"that raising taxes on wealthier Americans has to be part of any compromise","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"to resolve the crisis","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"and ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"emboldened by election gains in the House and Senate ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"Reid said","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"Republicans `` ca n't push us around '' on the issue .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"`` There was a message","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"sent to us by the American people ,","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"based on the campaign , ''","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"Reid said at a news conference .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"`` People","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"making all this money","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"have to contribute a little bit more . ''","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"In his speech , Boehner said","depth":5},{"id":90,"text":"he hopes","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"an agreement can be reached `` that sends a signal to our economy , and to the world ,","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"that after years of punting on the major fiscal challenges","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"we face ,","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"2013 is going to be different . ''","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"But he also said","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"he did n't think","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"a deal could be struck in the next month and a half during a lame duck session of Congress .","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Instead , he wants to reach an agreement with Democrats on a framework or bridge","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"that would postpone the cuts and tax-rate changes for one year","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"until a broader deal on deficit reduction","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"-- including entitlement and tax reform --","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"can be worked out .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"That 's at odds with Reid","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"who said","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"he opposes `` kicking the can down the road '' anymore .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"`` Waiting for a month , six weeks , six months , that 's not going to solve the problem , ''","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"Reid said .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"`` We know what needs to be done .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"So , I think","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"that we should just roll up our sleeves","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"and get it done . ''","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"Boehner and top House GOP leaders held a conference call with all House Republicans","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"shortly before the speaker made his speech .","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"According to two participants on the call","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"the speaker gave a full readout of what he planned to say publicly ,","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"and","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"while he reinforced his pledge","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"not to agree to tax increases ,","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"he did urge rank and file members to give him some room","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"to negotiate with the White House .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"A senior GOP aide said","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"that the ideas","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"that Boehner outlined in his speech Wednesday","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"were similar to the revenue proposal","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"that Pennsylvania GOP Sen. Pat Toomey and other Republicans on the `` supercommittee '' offered last summer .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"`` This is the framework","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"that everyone has been talking about , ''","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"the aide said ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"and admitted ,","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"referring to the two parties ' differences on the details on the revenue side .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"`` We have n't been able to thread the needle yet . ''","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"Boehner 's spokesman said","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"there are no meetings scheduled yet between the speaker and the president ,","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"and reiterated","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"that any deal needs to be hashed out between the principals , not in a public back-and-forth series of photo ops .","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"Senate Republican Leader Mitch McConnell reinforced Boehner 's opposition to higher tax rates","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"and he argued","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"it 's up to President Obama to `` propose a way","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"for both parties to work together","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"in avoiding the fiscal cliff","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"without harming a weak and fragile economy . '' `` Now is the time","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"for the President to propose solutions","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"that actually have a chance","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"of passing the Republican-controlled House and a closely-divided Senate , ''","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"McConnell said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"To that point , a top Senate GOP aide argued","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"that many of the Democrats","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"who won Senate seats Tuesday in swing states like North Dakota , Montana , Virginia and West Virginia ,","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"did n't campaign on raising top rates .","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"The aide said","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"there are several moderate Democrats from GOP-leaning states","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"up for re-election in two years","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"who will chafe against raising taxes .","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"President Obama weighed in as well","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"by placing separate calls to Reid , Boehner , McConnell , and House Democratic Leader Nancy Pelosi .","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"The White House said","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"he told them","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"tax increases for wealthy Americans need to be part of a deal","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"avoid the fiscal cliff","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"and reduce the debt .","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"Speak","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"ng to the seriousness","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"iven to his speech ,","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"oehner employed a teleprompter","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"o help him deliver it smoothly .","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"uch devices , popular with presidents , are rarely used on Capitol Hill .","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"he speaker did not take any questions","depth":8},{"id":168,"text":"hen it ended .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":337,"left":0,"right":336,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":336,"left":256,"right":335,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":256,"left":171,"right":255,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"par